Package: repg
Type: Package
Title: Wrapper Functions To Connect To PostgreSQL Databases
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Are Strom
Maintainer: Are Strom <are.strom@gmail.com>
Description: A collection of functions to securely connect to PostgreSQL databases using 
    credentials stored in .Renviron. Avoids the need to supply usernames or password in
    code. Also avoids potential for accidentally exposing credentials when sharing or
    posting code to GitHub.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Depends: R (>= 3.4.1)
Imports:
    DBI (>= 0.7),
    RPostgres (>= 0.1-4)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
